                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6630" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1041</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8165 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顺势而为：中芯国际的A股回归之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Follow the trend: SMIC&#39;s A-share return</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王洪生，张焕晨，谷海芸，廖丹妮，赵安起，朱萌萌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东农业大学*</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绍兴中芯集成电路制造股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中芯国际；交叉上市；科创板；A股</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SMIC International; Cross listing; Scientific innovation board; A shares</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2004年中芯国际在香港联合证券交易所和美国纽交所上市，而接下来却面临着中概股境外上市后普遍存在的问题--估值不尽人意，投资者的投资热情低迷；遭受到行政打压甚至制裁，以及做空机构的恶意做空；企业维持上市的成本高昂等。而随着中国资本市场的不断发展与完善，境外上市的红筹股回归国内必然是大势所趋。中芯国际于2020年7月回归A股，在上交所科创板上市。本案例介绍了中芯国际企业从初创到发展，克服困境实现技术起步与发展的全过程，以及公司实现境外与境内上市融资的经历。引导学生掌握交叉上市、科创板上市融资的相关知识点，以及红筹股企业国内上市的决策要点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2004, SMIC was listed on the stock exchange of Hong Kong and the New York Stock Exchange of the United States, but then it faced the common problems after the overseas listing of zhonggai shares - unsatisfactory valuation and low investment enthusiasm of investors; Suffer from strong repression, and even suffer from malicious shorting by shorting institutions; The high cost of maintaining the listing of enterprises. With the improvement of China&#39;s capital market system, it is the general trend for red chips to return to a shares. In July 2020, SMIC was listed on the science and Innovation Board of Shanghai Stock Exchange and returned to a shares. This case introduces the whole process of SMIC from start-up to development, overcoming difficulties and realizing technology start-up and development, as well as the company&#39;s experience of overseas and domestic listing and financing. Guide students to master the relevant knowledge points of cross listing, listing and financing of science and innovation board, as well as the key decision points of domestic listing of red chip enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融市场与金融机构》、《金融市场学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IPO上市理论及上市地点选择；科创板和交叉上市理论；中国存托凭证和分拆上市理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
